---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import TeamSection from '../../components/TeamSection.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us & Team" description="Learn about the founding principles, mission, and legal team of NS Law & Consultancy.">
  
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-navy-950 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-gold-500/10 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-6 relative z-10 animate-fade-in">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl font-serif font-bold tracking-tight">
        <span class="text-gradient-gold">Our Principles</span>
      </h1>
      <div class="w-20 h-0.5 bg-gold-500 mx-auto"></div>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-cream-200 font-light leading-relaxed">
        Guided by the rule of law and universal standards of justice, we offer strategic legal consultancy to multinational enterprises and individuals.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gold-500/50 to-transparent z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- Principles Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-cream-100 dark:bg-navy-900 transition-colors">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-16">
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-glass-card p-8 rounded-lg space-y-4 border border-navy-900/5 dark:border-white/5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded bg-navy-900 text-gold-400 flex items-center justify-center font-serif font-bold text-xl">01</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-navy-900 dark:text-cream-100">Integrity & Transparency</h3>
          <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-navy-700 dark:text-cream-300/80 leading-relaxed font-light">
            Our attorney-client relationships are built on unwavering trust and transparent communication, ensuring predictable legal pathways.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-glass-card p-8 rounded-lg space-y-4 border border-navy-900/5 dark:border-white/5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded bg-navy-900 text-gold-400 flex items-center justify-center font-serif font-bold text-xl">02</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-navy-900 dark:text-cream-100">Preventive Law</h3>
          <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-navy-700 dark:text-cream-300/80 leading-relaxed font-light">
            While meticulously resolving our clients' existing disputes, we proactively anticipate future legal risks to build a comprehensive protective shield.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-glass-card p-8 rounded-lg space-y-4 border border-navy-900/5 dark:border-white/5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded bg-navy-900 text-gold-400 flex items-center justify-center font-serif font-bold text-xl">03</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-navy-900 dark:text-cream-100">Global Perspective</h3>
          <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-navy-700 dark:text-cream-300/80 leading-relaxed font-light">
            With deep expertise in both Turkish legislation and international frameworks (GDPR, international arbitration, cross-border commerce), we deliver borderless solutions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Quote Box -->
      <div class="p-10 rounded-xl bg-navy-950 text-cream-100 border border-gold-500/30 text-center space-y-6 shadow-2xl">
        <h3 class="font-serif italic text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-gold-400">
          "Honeste vivere, alterum non laedere, suum cuique tribuere."
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-cream-200 font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          This ancient maxim of Roman law — <strong class="text-white">"To live honorably, not to injure another, and to render to each his own"</strong> — serves as the fundamental compass for all our legal operations at NS Law & Consultancy.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Section -->
  <TeamSection />

</Layout>
